====================  Classes in HTML   ========================================
<h2 class="dark-orange"> Classes in Html</h2>
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------




================= CSS Stylesheet  ==============================================

*** Class selector ***
.dark-orange {   		//    .	<--- the dot operator selects the "class"
	color: darkorange;
}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

*** ID selector ***
#							<--- selects the "id" tags
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

*** h2 selector ***
h2 {						<--- selects all the h2 elements
	font-family: sans-serif;

}
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------














































